																						<h2 class="title">Don’t ban biking during the coronavirus pandemic</h2>
													</div>
					</div>
									<div class="item ">
						<div class="item-wrapper">
															<a href="https://calmatters.org/politics/california-legislature/2020/04/california-senate-hearing-coronavirus-budget-oversight/" class="link thumb" aria-label="Read more about California senators frustrated by few answers,  tech glitches in virtual hearing on coronavirus spending">
									<div class="thumb-inner">
										<img width="321" height="214" src="https://calmatters.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/04/AP_pool_CoronavirusOversight_06.jpg?fit=321%2C214" class="attachment-medium-wide-rec size-medium-wide-rec wp-post-image" alt="Senators Jim Nielson, left, and Holly Mitchell, right, sit six feet apart, as they view a large video screen during a hearing of the special subcommittee on COVID-19 on April 16, 2020. Lawmakers are looking into how Gov. Gavin Newsom has been spending money to address the new coronavirus crisis. Due to the unusual circumstances only Nielsen, vice chair of the committee and Mitchell, chair of the committee, attended the hearing in person while other committee members, those testifying and the public joined by video. Photo by Rich Pedroncelli, AP Photo/Pool" srcset="https://calmatters.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/04/AP_pool_CoronavirusOversight_06.jpg?w=2000 2000w, https://calmatters.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/04/AP_pool_CoronavirusOversight_06.jpg?w=300 300w, https://calmatters.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/04/AP_pool_CoronavirusOversight_06.jpg?w=768 768w, https://calmatters.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/04/AP_pool_CoronavirusOversight_06.jpg?w=1024 1024w, https://calmatters.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/04/AP_pool_CoronavirusOversight_06.jpg?w=1536 1536w, https://calmatters.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/04/AP_pool_CoronavirusOversight_06.jpg?w=460 460w, https://calmatters.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/04/AP_pool_CoronavirusOversight_06.jpg?w=321 321w, https://calmatters.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/04/AP_pool_CoronavirusOversight_06.jpg?w=780 780w, https://calmatters.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/04/AP_pool_CoronavirusOversight_06.jpg?w=858 858w, https://calmatters.org/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2020/04/AP_pool_CoronavirusOversight_06.jpg?w=793 793w" sizes="(max-width: 321px) 100vw, 321px" />									</div>
